---
// SecretsChecklist.astro — Implementation checklist
---
<div class="scl-wrap">
  <h3 class="scl-title">Implementation Checklist</h3>
  <div class="scl-items">
    <div class="scl-item scl-i1"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Run `git log --all -p | grep -i "password\|secret\|api_key"` — clean history if needed</span></div>
    <div class="scl-item scl-i2"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Add pre-commit hook with gitleaks or trufflehog — block secrets before they're committed</span></div>
    <div class="scl-item scl-i3"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Migrate all .env secrets to Vault / AWS Secrets Manager / Doppler</span></div>
    <div class="scl-item scl-i4"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Unique secrets per environment — dev, staging, prod NEVER share credentials</span></div>
    <div class="scl-item scl-i5"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Enable audit logging — know WHO accessed WHAT secret WHEN</span></div>
    <div class="scl-item scl-i6"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Set up automatic rotation with dual-active grace period</span></div>
    <div class="scl-item scl-i7"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Least privilege — services only access secrets they need. No wildcard policies.</span></div>
    <div class="scl-item scl-i8"><span class="scl-check">☐</span><span class="scl-text">Incident playbook — if a secret leaks, rotate ALL secrets in that scope within 1 hour</span></div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .scl-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .scl-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .scl-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
  .scl-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;padding:8px 12px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.12);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #334155;opacity:0;animation:sclIn .3s ease forwards}
  .scl-i1{animation-delay:.05s}.scl-i2{animation-delay:.1s}.scl-i3{animation-delay:.15s}.scl-i4{animation-delay:.2s}.scl-i5{animation-delay:.25s}.scl-i6{animation-delay:.3s}.scl-i7{animation-delay:.35s}.scl-i8{animation-delay:.4s}
  @keyframes sclIn{to{opacity:1}}
  .scl-check{color:#4ade80;font-size:.8rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}.scl-text{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.5}
</style>
